Package org.cougaar.planning.servlet.data.completion

Class Summary
AbstractTask Represents an abstract Task entry within the COMPLETION PSP.
CompletionData Abstract representation of the data leaving the Completion PSP.
CompletionDataFactory Factory that produces sub-objects based on tags and attributes for CompletionData
FailedTask Represents a "failed" Task.
FullCompletionData Represents the data leaving the Completion PSP -- FullCompletionData captures all the AbstractTasks.
SimpleCompletionData Represents the data leaving the Completion PSP -- SimpleCompletionData only contains counters of the Tasks, not AbstractTasks.
UnconfidentTask Represents an "unconfident" (less-than-100%-confidence) Task.
UnestimatedTask Represents an "unestimated" Task.
UnplannedTask Represents an "unplanned" Task.
